    "One example of this is the combination of text, image, and speech data.",
    "By combining these many data kinds, multimodal learning approaches enable more thorough analysis and deeper interactions.",
    "A system might, for instance, use a combination of image recognition, NLP, and speech recognition to analyse a video (to identify objects, transcribe spoken words, and interpret context) (Baltrušaitis et al., 2018).",
